reviews.review_text:
my first show clearly remember digging the Truckin' / 'jam' and when I heard the Dark Star opening I thought it would be a 20-30 minute one -but no -it was a short and sweet like the original 45 ...I was in the balcony -I yelled "Alligator!' ..a head walking by said politely- "they don't play that anymore" 
I replied-"That's ok -they can't hear me." 

thinking that the Dead didn't need another chief in their kitchen -they knew all the ingredients 
had a real good time
car in parking lot wouldn't start on snowy night 2 cars offered help I was impressed with the folks and wanted go with them...>
